START
Display message: "Enter your score"
Get input from the user and store it as 'score'
IF score is between 70 and 100
    THEN grade = "A" 
ELSE IF score is between 60 and 69
    THEN grade = "B"
ELSE IF score is between 50 and 59
    THEN grade = "C"
ELSE IF score is between 45 and 49
    THEN grade = "D" 
ELSE IF score is between 40 and 44
    THEN grade = "E"
ELSE IF grade is between 0 and 39
    THEN grade = "F"
ELSE
    grade = "Invalid score"
Display message: "Your score is: " followed by the grade
END